Package ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.AssetTrading

Class TradeHistory

java.lang.Object
ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.AssetTrading.TradeHistory
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class TradeHistory
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Class for creating an TradeHistory object which is used to fetch history of any trades completed via the MarketplaceHistoryDataSource in which this interacts with the Marketplace_history database tables directly.
